          },
          {
            "allowLineSplit": true,
            "content": "Once the text cursor clears the bottom of the float, the full column width is restored and the layout continues as normal. The line-width variance visible in the wrapped lines versus the lines below the float confirms that the SpatialMap is correctly reporting a narrowed interval only for the lines that coexist vertically with the obstacle. No element boundary coincides with the float boundary: the same text box holds both narrow and full-width lines, distinguished only by per-line data in the _lineWidths array.",
